    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Material derived from stems of various species of the genera Scirpus, used for making strong mats, chair seats, hats, and basketry. For material from species in the genus Typha, use "cattail." </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
